export const projects = [
{
    title: "Pitch App", 
    image:"./photos/pitch.jpg",
    subtite: "NSBE LinkedIn Hackathon Project", 
    description: `As short-form video content rises in popularity due to apps like TikTok and Triller, 
                  social media is shifting from just pictures and text-based apps. Short-form video content 
                  should eventually be something professional platforms consider implementing as traditional 
                  modes of job searching have become more digital. How might we do this? We are all familiar 
                  with the brief speech that happens within 20 to 30 seconds in professional environments 
                  called an elevator pitch. An elevator pitch is a simple and direct opportunity for job 
                  seekers to share their skills more engagingly. Pitch would be a short-form video platform 
                  for recruiters to seek out potential employees aside from viewing just resumes and profiles.`, 
    link: "https://pitch30.community/"
}, 


]; 

export const skills = [
        "HTML/CSS",
        "JavaScript", 
        "React.js",
        ".Net", 
        "Bootstrap", 
        "Node.js", 
        "C++", 
        "Java"
];
